and I think
they'll expect a tip,
so give them 50 cents

748
00:46:09,180 --> 00:46:10,169
Apiece?

749
00:46:11,749 --> 00:46:14,047
I'll leave that
to your own judgment,
Sergeant

750
00:46:14,118 --> 00:46:16,018
In the meantime,
I'll be in the car

751
00:46:21,325 --> 00:46:24,726
He came in just before
closing time on Saturday
and bought the watch

752
00:46:24,795 --> 00:46:27,821
Very similar to yours
Works the same
Only the case is different

753
00:46:27,898 --> 00:46:30,492
Well, my watch
I was just wondering
if you knew about this

754
00:46:30,568 --> 00:46:33,264
My watch
lost a day yesterday

755
00:46:33,671 --> 00:46:36,299
I was wondering,
do you
No It didn't lose a day

756
