Now, last month had 30 days

758
00:46:42,213 --> 00:46:44,340
Does your watch say the first
instead of the second?

759
00:46:46,050 --> 00:46:47,142
Yes, the first

760
00:46:47,218 --> 00:46:48,207
Here Give it to me

761
00:46:48,686 --> 00:46:50,483
You see,
in a 30day month,

762
00:46:50,554 --> 00:46:52,954
you have to turn your watch
24 hours ahead,

763
00:46:53,023 --> 00:46:55,787
or else it'll say the 31st
instead of the first

