00:48:03,961 --> 00:48:05,622
Hi, Miss Lytton

787
00:48:06,697 --> 00:48:08,688
Lieutenant You look
in high spirits

788
00:48:08,999 --> 00:48:11,263
Oh, I am, Miss Lytton
I am

789
00:48:11,335 --> 00:48:13,496
It turns out we may
be right after all

790
00:48:14,371 --> 00:48:18,808
Shaeffer told everybody
that he was leaving for
the islands the next day

791
00:48:19,743 --> 00:48:22,974
Is it part of your job
to trip people up?
Or to see if you can?

792
00:48:24,515 --> 00:48:26,039
Trip people up?

793
00:48:27,117 --> 00:48:28,744
Trip people up

794
00:48:29,353 --> 00:48:32,117
We never thought
that Mr Shaeffer was
leaving the next day

795
00:48:32,623 --> 00:48:35,456
You may recall
I thought exactly
the opposite

796
00:48:36,627 --> 00:48:40,256
Gee, I forgot about that
I get confused sometimes,
you know?

797
00:48:40,331 --> 00:48:43,596
I mean, just trying to keep
all the facts straight
in my head

798
00:48:44,134 --> 00:48:47,968
Lieutenant, you must
never underestimate me

799
00:48:48,973 --> 00:48:49,962
Nor I you

800
00:48:50,741 --> 00:48:53,107
I don't in the least mind
you playing tricks,

801
00:48:53,577 --> 00:48:56,740
but you're going to have to be
a little cleverer, aren't you?

802
00:48:56,814 --> 00:49:00,580
I knew yesterday
that you were going to have
to interrogate us, all of us,

803
00:49:00,651 --> 00:49:03,279
because we are, all of us,
of course, under suspicion

804
00:49:04,321 --> 00:49:05,811
You have to be suspicious

805
00:49:06,790 --> 00:49:08,223
That's part of your job

806
00:49:08,959 --> 00:49:12,395
Well, I have to ask questions,
if that's what you mean

807
00:49:12,463 --> 00:49:14,931
I wouldn't say
that I was suspicious

808
00:49:16,467 --> 00:49:18,492
Your delicacy
does you credit

809
00:49:19,103 --> 00:49:20,900
You'd best save it
for my sister

810
00:49:21,505 --> 00:49:23,097
I'm afraid
you're going to need it

811
00:49:23,607 --> 00:49:25,404
She won't faint again,
will she?

812
00:49:27,278 --> 00:49:28,973
I know it's

813
00:49:30,581 --> 00:49:33,072
I know it's
