without certain influence,
Lieutenant Columbus

1016
01:00:07,083 --> 01:00:09,278
MILLER: Lieutenant Columbo,
can I see you a moment?

1017
01:00:22,198 --> 01:00:25,463
I found this dish
in her room,
hidden on a shelf

1018
01:00:30,040 --> 01:00:31,234
That's it

