when I killed him
and Uncle Edward

1085
01:04:20,236 --> 01:04:21,703
Is that true?

1086
01:04:22,405 --> 01:04:25,374
You think it is,
so what's the difference?

1087
01:04:25,542 --> 01:04:28,841
It's gonna make
a difference in court
if you talk like that

1088
01:04:28,912 --> 01:04:31,039
