1098
01:05:02,946 --> 01:05:05,312
Well, that's open
to question, isn't it?

1099
01:05:05,381 --> 01:05:08,509
I don't understand
what this has to do
with anything

1100
01:05:09,352 --> 01:05:15,313
Now, you don't have to answer
any of my questions without
a lawyer unless you want to

1101
01:05:17,026 --> 01:05:19,187
