on a Thursday

1104
01:05:26,035 --> 01:05:30,096
It was June 28th,
and they didn't come back
until after you were born

1105
01:05:30,573 --> 01:05:35,272
And you were
born on December 27th,
two days after Christmas

1106
01:05:36,879 --> 01:05:38,471
What is that?

1107
01:05:38,581 --> 01:05:42,073
That's a copy
of your birth certificate
It's on file in Sacramento

1108
01:05:43,519 --> 01:05:47,922
It means that Mrs Brandt
was three months pregnant
when they eloped

1109
01:05:48,791 --> 01:05:51,191
Did you know that,
or didn't you?

1110
01:05:51,494 --> 01:05:56,454
Lieutenant, what happened then
is nobody's business anymore

1111
01:05:56,966 --> 01:06:00,094
except for my mother's
and my Aunt Ruth's

1112
01:06:00,803 --> 01:06:02,498
If I never talked
to them about it,

1113
01:06:03,206 --> 01:06:04,639
why should I talk to you?

1114
01:06:06,576 --> 01:06:09,238
You love your Aunt Ruth
a lot, don't you?

1115
01:06:09,946 --> 01:06:11,470
More than your mother

1116
01:06:12,415 --> 01:06:16,010
Maybe more than anybody
You wouldn't like to see her
get hurt, would you?

1117
01:06:16,719 --> 01:06:19,813
She must have been
hurt plenty back then

1118
01:06:20,223 --> 01:06:23,556
Enough so that she got left
without anything, right?

1119
01:06:25,128 --> 01:06:27,187
Anything but the museum,
that is

1120
01:06:28,064 --> 01:06:29,463
What do you want?

1121
01:06:29,899 --> 01:06:32,026
You were only seven
when your father died

1122
01:06:32,335 --> 01:06:33,666
He died of a heart attack,
didn't he?

1123
01:06:34,904 --> 01:06:36,701
That's what
the coroner's report said

1124
01:06:37,940 --> 01:06:39,373
That he'd had
two heart attacks,

1125
01:06:39,442 --> 01:06:40,704
that he was under
a doctor's care,

1126
01:06:40,777 --> 01:06:42,108
and there was no autopsy

1127
01:06:42,912 --> 01:06:45,210
Your Aunt Ruth said that
your mother wouldn't
hear of it

1128
01:06:45,281 --> 01:06:49,547
And the doctor probably
didn't see any reason
for an autopsy anyway

1129
01:06:52,755 --> 01:06:55,189
How can you be so positive
about all that?

1130
01:06:55,258 --> 01:06:58,091
When I saw your Aunt Ruth
the other day,

1131
01:06:58,261 --> 01:07:01,719
she began talking
about your father
and his death

1132
01:07:02,932 --> 01:07:05,867
Your Uncle Edward's death
reminded her of it

1133
01:07:06,969 --> 01:07:10,530
So? Death always
reminds you of death

1134
01:07:10,606 --> 01:07:14,235
Right And murder
reminds you of murder

1135
01:07:14,410 --> 01:07:17,675
Even when you don't know it,
you begin to think it

1136
01:07:18,614 --> 01:07:20,411
I don't know what you mean

1137
01:07:21,184 --> 01:07:22,173
Don't you?

1138
01:07:22,485 --> 01:07:25,682
He died of a heart attack
Everyone knows that

1139
01:07:26,389 --> 01:07:30,655
Heart attacks can be
made to happen in a lot
of different ways, Janie

1140
01:07:30,993 --> 01:07:35,054
Do you know that digitalis
and quinidine can have
a reverse effect

1141
01:07:35,264 --> 01:07:36,856
if the dose is too high?

1142
01:07:37,734 --> 01:07:41,864
And it needn't even be
that high a dose
if a man has a weak heart

1143
01:07:42,905 --> 01:07:46,898
The coroner's report
on your father said
that his condition was bad,

1144
01:07:47,710 --> 01:07:50,178
and that he had other
minor complications

1145
01:07:50,246 --> 01:07:51,235
Not big ones

1146
01:07:51,447 --> 01:07:53,142
Little ones
that the doctor knew about,

1147
01:07:53,216 --> 01:07:56,276
and your Aunt Ruth knew about
because she was nursing him

1148
01:07:56,853 --> 01:07:58,218
He had asthma,

1149
01:07:58,354 --> 01:08:00,288
he was susceptible
to infection,

1150
01:08:00,957 --> 01:08:03,585
it's why he had a bad cold
the week that he died

1151
01:08:05,194 --> 01:08:06,456
So what?

1152
01:08:06,529 --> 01:08:10,090
So she probably gave him
a lot of chamomile tea

1153
01:08:21,077 --> 01:08:23,068
It was a lovely
funeral service

1154
01:08:23,146 --> 01:08:24,135
Lovely

1155
